20they're%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20QBS%20would%20mark%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20AWS's%20AI%20application%20strategy.%20Amazon%20rolled%20out%20Q%20Business%20last%20year%20as%20its%20premier%20AI%20assistant%20for%20professional%20users%2C%20but%20the%20product%20faced%20early%20challenges%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-q-chatbot-launch-rushed-flawed-anthropic-claude-ai-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erushed%3C%2Fa%3E%20debut%2C%20BI%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-q-ai-early-challenges-aws-chatbot-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20Q%20Business%20app%20falling%20short%20of%20internal%20sales%20targets%2C%20AWS%20is%20expected%20to%20prioritize%20QBS%2C%20according%20to%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20hasn't%20decided%20on%20the%20external%20brand%20of%20QBS%2C%20but%20%26quot%3BQuick%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20the%20names%20being%20considered%2C%20these%20people%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AWS%20CEO%20Matt%20Garman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674a41049f2901eb6037b6c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221938%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAWS%20CEO%20Matt%20Garman%3Cp%3EJOSH%20EDELSON%2FAFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20is%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20growth%26quot%3B%20for%20Q%20Business%2C%20with%20customers%20such%20as%20Nasdaq%2C%20Smartsheet%2C%20and%20the%20NFL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anything%2C%20we%20are%20investing%20even%20more%20in%20this%20area%20and%20expect%20to%20be%20delivering%20a%20ton%20of%20new%20features%20and%20capabilities%20over%20the%20coming%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ed1c13c-18a5-4d20-989d-34f474e87f13%5C%22%3E'Single%20entry%20point'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20internal%20documents%2C%20QBS%20aims%20to%20provide%20a%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20interface%26quot%3B%20for%20accessing%20data%20across%20various%20business%20applications%20such%20as%20Asana%20and%20Microsoft%20Excel.%20It%20will%20be%20capable%20of%20responding%20to%20queries%20and%20automating%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20closing%20a%20Salesforce%20ticket%20or%20sending%20an%20Outlook%20email%2C%20enabling%20%26quot%3Bagentic%26quot%3B%20workflows%2C%20the%20documents%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20theoretical%20example%20outlined%20involves%20a%20business%20manager%20asking%20QBS%20for%20recent%20sales%20figures%20in%20a%20specific%20region.%20Drawing%20on%20Salesforce%20data%2C%20QBS%20can%20deliver%20insights%20on%20sales%20performance%2C%20top%20customers%2C%20and%20potential%20deals.%20The%20manager%20can%20then%20generate%20a%20report%20with%20this%20information%20and%20email%20it%20to%20their%20boss%2C%20all%20within%20the%20same%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20sees%20QBS%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20a%20widespread%20challenge%20faced%20by%20business%20users%3A%20securely%20connecting%20various%20tools%20with%20existing%20business%20data%20and%20automating%20tasks%20with%20AI.%20Companies%20can%20spend%20months%20setting%20up%20even%20basic%20integrations%2C%20often%20relying%20on%20external%20technical%20partners%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20business%20users%20frequently%20waste%20time%20juggling%20multiple%20applications%2C%20manually%20building%20workflows%2C%20or%20copying%20and%20pasting%20information%20to%20complete%20tasks.%20This%20fragmented%20approach%20results%20in%20%26quot%3Bduplicative%20work%2C%20inconsistent%20experiences%2C%20and%20errors%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20Amazon%20documents%20noted%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20teams%20to%20standardize%20and%20streamline%20new%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20physical%20stores%20VP%20Dilip%20Kumar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F619408a5a2e68800198a874d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAWS%20VP%20Dilip%20Kumar%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FTed%20S.%20Warren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22132d99d6-db5d-4d63-bfef-58d9fd4d4810%5C%22%3E'Unify%20all%20products'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQBS%20is%20Amazon's%20latest%20bid%20to%20break%20into%20the%20business%20application%20market%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20software-as-a-service.%20While%20Amazon%20dominates%20cloud%20infrastructure%2C%20such%20as%20storage%20and%20compute%2C%20it%20has%20long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-aws-struggles-in-saas-business-applications-cloud-market-hubspot-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estruggled%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20gain%20traction%20in%20the%20SaaS%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20AWS%20Connect%2C%20one%20of%20its%20business%20applications%20targeting%20customer%20support%20agents%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Btens%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20customers%20and%20more%20than%2010%20million%20contact%20center%20interactions%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQBS%20isn't%20the%20only%20business%20application%20Amazon%20is%20working%20on.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20build%20a%20new%20AI%20coding%20assistant%2C%20internally%20codenamed%20%26quot%3BKiro%2C%26quot%3B%20BI%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-kiro-project-ai-agents-software-coding-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQBS%20also%20comes%20as%20AI%20increasingly%20lowers%20the%20barrier%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-tools-buy-versus-build-software-saas-netlify-bolt-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%3C%2Fa%3E%20custom%20software.%20Amazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20wrote%20in%20a%20companywide%20email%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20company%20intends%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20build%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAWS%20VP%20Dilip%20Kumar%20is%20overseeing%20the%20QBS%20project%2C%20the%20documents%20said.%20Kumar%2C%20who%20previously%20launched%20Amazon's%20Just%20Walk%20Out%20cashierless%20technology%2C%20recently%20combined%20the%20Q%20and%20Quicksight%20teams%20under%20a%20single%20organization%2C%20the%20people%20familiar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20been%20targeting%20a%20July%20launch%20for%20QBS%2C%20but%20that%20timeline%20could%20change%2C%20these%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20plans%20to%20make%20QBS%20accessible%20with%20existing%20user%20credentials%20for%20Q%20Business%20or%20QuickSight%2C%20one%20of%20the%20documents%20stated.%20The%20company%20expects%20users%20to%20%26quot%3Bappreciate%20the%20consolidated%20onboarding%20and%20subscription%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long%20run%2C%20Amazon%20wants%20QBS%20to%20%26quot%3Bunify%20all%20products%26quot%3B%20under%20one%20umbrella%2C%20featuring%20a%20shared%20identity%20and%20governance%20framework%2C%20along%20with%20seamless%20integration%20across%20its%20various%20capabilities%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20documents%20obtained%20by%20BI%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aekim%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eekim%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%2C%20Telegram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp%20at%20650-942-3061.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5