edia%20and%20entertainment%20dealmaking%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20podcast%2C%20Blitzer%20sat%20down%20with%20hosts%20Alex%20Rodriguez%20and%20Jason%20Kelly%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20empire%20of%20team%20ownerships%20he%20has%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlitzer%20is%20the%20cofounder%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20Harris%20Blitzer%20Sports%20and%20Entertainment%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20NBA's%20Philadelphia%2076ers%20and%20the%20NHL's%20New%20Jersey%20Devils.%20He%20also%20holds%20stakes%20in%20the%20NFL's%20Washington%20Commanders%2C%20the%20MLB's%20Cleveland%20Guardians%2C%20and%20the%20MLS's%20Real%20Salt%20Lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20an%20investor%20in%20any%20of%20these%20teams%20and%20leagues%20is%20fun%2C%20it's%20rewarding%2C%20it's%20challenging%2C%20it's%20really%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20Blitzer%20Sports%20and%20Entertainment%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20additional%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6940844-937a-4106-988b-2577000a1288%5C%22%3EWhy%20Blizter%20is%20betting%20on%20sports%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBlitzer's%20first%20sports%20investment%20was%20with%20Josh%20Harris%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Apollo%2C%20in%202011%20when%20they%20acquired%20the%20Philadelphia%2076ers%20for%20%24280%20million.%20Together%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjosh-harris-net-worth-profile-apollo-cofounder-mets-potential-owner-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethey%20founded%3C%2Fa%3E%20Harris%20Blitzer%20Sports%20%26amp%3B%20Entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20in%20corporate%20carve-outs.%20We%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20in%20bringing%20in%20new%20management%20teams%20and%20thinking%20about%20incentive%20structures%20in%20ways%20that%20I%20don't%20really%20think%20sports%20had%20had%20really%20done%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Blitzer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20thesis%20for%20investing%20is%20the%20same%20one%20he%20has%20now%3A%20supply%20and%20demand%2C%20he%20said.%20There%20are%20a%20set%20number%20of%20sports%20teams%2C%20and%20more%20ultrawealthy%20people%20and%20newer%20entrants%2C%20like%20private%20equity%20firms%2C%20want%20to%20buy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20content%20and%20media%20businesses%2C%20and%20they%20have%20some%20of%20the%20best%20IP%20in%20the%20world.%20And%20frankly%2C%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20when%20you%20think%20about%20live%20content%2C%20there's%20probably%20nothing%20more%20valuable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20the%20first%20person%20to%20own%20equity%20in%20all%20five%20of%20the%20major%20men's%20sports%20leagues%20in%20the%20US.%20His%20portfolio%20is%20strategically%20broad%2C%20he%20said%2C%20so%20he%20can%20offer%20wide%2C%20cross-sport%20reach%20for%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20for%20example%2C%20they%20did%20a%20deal%20with%20Campbell's%20%E2%80%94%20the%20soup%20company%20%E2%80%94%20across%20the%20Commanders%2C%20the%20Sixers%2C%20the%20Devils%2C%20and%20Joe%20Gibbs%20Racing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20private%20equity%20portfolio%20companies%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20Blitzer's%20portfolio%20also%20allows%20the%20company%20to%20better%20spread%20the%20cost%20of%20cutting-edge%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20AI%20and%20data%20analytics%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlitzer%20is%20also%20betting%20on%20sports%20outside%20pro%20men's%20leagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Blitzer%20and%20Harris%20launched%20Unrivaled%20Sports%2C%20a%20company%20that%20specializes%20in%20youth%20sports.%20Blitzer%20also%20holds%20a%20stake%20in%20NWSL's%20Utah%20Royals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22052da815-9d3b-439c-a8cb-a9634873cb97%5C%22%3EBlitzer's%20advice%20to%20would-be%20sports%20owners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjosh-harris-net-worth-profile-apollo-cofounder-mets-potential-owner-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlitzer%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20a%20strategic%2C%20portfolio%20approach%20to%20investing%20in%20sport%2C%20he%20points%20out%20that%20owning%20sports%20teams%20goes%20beyond%20crunching%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20his%20best%20advice%20for%20anyone%20investing%20in%20a%20sports%20franchise%20or%20a%20league%20is%20to%20go%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20do%20anything%20in%20your%20first%20season%2C%20like%20literally.%20Just%20learn.%20Just%20go%20around%20and%20meet%20everyone%20in%20the%20organization%2C%20watch%20what%20they%20do%2C%20how%20they%20do%20it.%20Do%20not%20come%20in%20and%20do%20big%20things%20in%20your%20first%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20before%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BBy%20the%20way%2C%20no%20one%20has%20taken%20that%20advice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-blitzer-blackstone-sports-investing-teams-nba-nhl-mlb-mls-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750403147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6854f707f748d8c055f4084b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-blitzer-blackstone-sports-investing-teams-nba-nhl-mlb-mls-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22David%20Blitzer%20is%20the%20the%20first%20person%20to%20own%20equity%20in%20all%20five%20of%20the%20major%20sports%20leagues%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ebrownstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Emmalyse%20Brownstein%2CHuileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-blitzer-blackstone-sports-investing-teams-nba-nhl-mlb-mls-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Inside%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Guy%20Pearce%20and%20Cosmo%20Jarvis%20A