r%20whose%20squad%20washed%20up%20in%20England%20after%20their%20boat%20sank.%20He%20saves%20them%20from%20a%20number%20of%20infected%2C%20but%20threatens%20to%20kill%20them%20when%20Isla%20helps%20a%20pregnant%20infected%20woman%20give%20birth%20to%20an%20uninfected%20baby.%20However%2C%20he's%20stopped%20by%20a%20variant%20of%20the%20infected%20called%20an%20Alpha%2C%20who%20rips%20Eric's%20head%20and%20spine%20off%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20escape%2C%20Kelson%20suddenly%20appears%20and%20drugs%20the%20Alpha%20(Chi%20Lewis-Parry)%20with%20a%20blowdart%2C%20and%20provides%20Spike%2C%20Isla%2C%20and%20the%20baby%20with%20sanctuary%20in%20an%20area%20where%20he%20has%20built%20huge%20towers%20out%20of%20bones%20and%20skulls.%20He%20calls%20it%20the%20%26quot%3BMemento%20Mori%2C%26quot%3B%20Latin%20for%20%26quot%3BRemember%20you%20die.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20film's%20quieter%20moments%2C%20he%20diagnoses%20Isla%20with%20cancer%2C%20which%20has%20spread%20to%20her%20brain.%20This%20explains%20her%20memory%20loss%20and%20extreme%20headaches.%20She%20chooses%20to%20let%20Kelson%20euthanize%20her%20and%20she%20tells%20Spike%20that%20she'll%20always%20be%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20walks%20off%20into%20the%20darkness%20with%20Kelson%2C%20and%20he%20returns%20with%20her%20skull.%20In%20a%20heartbreaking%20moment%2C%20he%20lets%20Spike%20pick%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20Memento%20Mori%20to%20place%20it%2C%20and%20he%20climbs%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20tower%2C%20positioning%20her%20skull%20so%20that%20she's%20forever%20looking%20out%20onto%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d6770f0-275d-44a0-b266-9ce39a099ed9%5C%22%3EAfter%20Isla's%20death%2C%20Spike%20embraces%20life%20on%20the%20mainland.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20older%20bald%20man%20hands%20a%20teenage%20boy%20a%20skull.%20On%20the%20left%2C%20the%20teenager%20is%20wearing%20a%20red%20sweater%20with%20a%20str