20cultural%20relevance%2C%20great%20product%2C%20great%20execution%2C%20and%20great%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgap-ceo-done-bombarding-consumers-with-promotions-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750379024000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68548d5e85e81483682c6e33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgap-ceo-done-bombarding-consumers-with-promotions-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gap's%20CEO%20on%20what%20the%20retailer%20got%20wrong%20in%20the%20past%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20plan%20to%20revitalize%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ebrownstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Emmalyse%20Brownstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgap-ceo-done-bombarding-consumers-with-promotions-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Ring%20of%20fire'%3A%20Israel%20says%20it%20flipped%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20war%20doctrine%3B%20IDF%20vows%20unrelenting%20pace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750378062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121963426%2Cimgsize-22778.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fring-of-fire-israel-says-it-flipped-irans-war-doctrine-idf-vows-unrelenting-pace%2Farticleshow%2F121963362.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F121963362.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELieutenant%20General%20Eyal%20Zamir%20announced%20that%20Israel%20has%20effectively%20turned%20Iran's%20'ring%20of%20fire'%20strategy%20against%20them%2C%20targeting%20Iranian%20assets%20within%20their%20own%20territory.%20Major%20General%20Shlomi%20Binder%20reported%20suc