0that%20we%20served%20our%20guests%2C%20and%20steel%20glasses%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365696%2Fonam-sadhya-recipes-avial-kalan-olan-erissery-palada-pradhaman-kerala-chef-pillai-shamees-kitchen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserve%20payasam%20and%20buttermilk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20the%20sadhya.%20True%20to%20our%20South%20Indian%20roots%2C%20we%20embraced%20banana%20leaves%20for%20serving%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20times%20when%20vendors%20were%20unsure%20about%20what%20we%20wanted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20wedding%20festivities%2C%20no%20plastic%20bottles%20were%20used.%20Instead%2C%20the%20couple%20set%20up%20water%20coolers%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20and%20the%20guests%20use%20glasses%20rather%20than%20disposable%20cups.%20At%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20wedding%20hall%2C%20guests%20were%20welcomed%20with%20cooling%20dispensers%20offering%20refreshing%20watermelon%20juice%20and%20lemonade%2C%20served%20in%20reusable%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20used%20palm%20leaf%20straws%20for%20the%20coconut%20water%20that%20they%20served%20to%20the%20guests%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078-300x157