0set%20up%20micro-warehouses%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20plans%20to%20expand%20operations%20soon%20to%20Nashik%20and%20Bengaluru.%20Their%20ambitions%20aren%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20just%20growing%20bigger%E2%80%94they%20want%20to%20grow%20better.%20Features%20like%20AI-based%20waste%20sorting%2C%20carbon%20footprint%20trackers%2C%20and%20formal%20tie-ups%20with%20municipal%20bodies%20are%20in%20the%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20create%20a%20nationwide%2C%20decentralised%20system%20for%20recycling%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayesh.%20%E2%80%9COne%20that%E2%80%99s%20accessible%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20completely%20transparent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStories%20from%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScrapdeal%E2%80%99s%20impact%20goes%20beyond%20just%20numbers.%20Its%20user%20reviews%20tell%20a%20story%20of%20growing%20environmental%20consciousness%20among%20everyday%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHave%20been%20their%20customer%20for%20many%20years%20now.%20They%20collect%20scrap%20from%20our%20society%20regularly.%20I%20had%20placed%20a%20request%20to%20collect%20my%204-wheeler%20tyres%2C%20and%20they%20came%20the%20very%20next%20day%20and%20gave%20the%20promised%20weighted%20price%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naveen%20Gupta%2C%20a%20Scrapdeal%20customer%2C%20shares%20with%20TBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20true%20sense%2C%20a%20service%20to%20society.%20People%20should%20support%20them.%20This%20will%20help%20them%20to%20achieve%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajesh%20Shekhawat.%20The%20team%20also%20conducts%20awareness%20sessions%20in%20schools%20and%20societies%2C%20encouraging%20citizens%20to%20embrace%20sustainable%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-59_