nt%20rapid%20growth.%20As%20the%20products%20started%20resonating%20with%20people%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20the%20gradual%20growth%20happening%20organically.%E2%80%9D%20Soorya%20joined%20the%20brand%20full-time%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESourcing%20raw%20ingredients%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20plant-based%20protein%20isn%E2%80%99t%20like%20anything%20else%20out%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soorya%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20focused%20on%20creating%20a%20product%20that%20was%20not%20only%20easy%20to%20digest%20but%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F286220%2Fbest-natural-chemical-free-home-floor-appliance-cleaners-buy-amazon-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20of%20common%20allergens%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20lot%20of%20plant-based%20proteins%20out%20there%20can%20cause%20bloating%2C%20and%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20that.%20Our%20formula%20includes%20digestive%20herbs%20like%20fennel%20and%20ginger%20to%20support%20gut%20health%20naturally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20utilises%20raw%20and%20ethically%20sourced%20herbs%20such%20as%3Cem%3E%20ashwagandha%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20turmeric%2C%20and%20ginger%2C%20each%20known%20for%20its%20anti-inflammatory%20and%20health-boosting%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20products%20that%20use%20artificial%20flavouring%2C%20Cosmix%20uses%20real%20ingredients%20such%20as%20vanilla%20beans%20and%20cocoa%20powder.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20very%20particular%20about%20the%20ingredients%20we%20use%20and%20where%20they%20come%20from%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vibha%20while%20explaining%20how%2