Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T204026.038_11zon-1750173039-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T204026.038_11zon-1750173039-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T204026.038_11zon-1750173039-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T204026.038_11zon-1750173039-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-451020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECosmix%20uses%20biodegradable%20scoops%20to%20combat%20the%20growing%20plastic%20problem%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBiodegradable%20scoops%20reduce%20the%20plastic%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPackaging%20produces%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fourworldindata.org%2Fdata-insights%2Fpackaging-is-the-source-of-40-of-the-planets-plastic-waste%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40%20percent%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20plastic%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20wanted%20to%20commit%20not%20only%20to%20wellness%20but%20also%20to%20being%20mindful%20of%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20to%20preserve%20the%20planet%E2%80%99s%20life.%20As%20they%20began%20building%20Cosmix%2C%20they%20realised%20that%20sustainability%20had%20to%20be%20a%20core%20part%20of%20their%20ethos.%20In%20an%20industry%20where%20plastic%20packaging%20and%20waste%20were%20rampant%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%20by%20offering%20an%20environmentally%20conscious%20alternative.%20The%20solution%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20biodegradable%20scoops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlastic%20scoops%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wasteful%20parts%20of%20protein%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soorya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20different.%20From%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20chose%20glass%20jars%20for%20our%20packaging%2C%20even%20though%20plastic%20was%20cheaper%20and%20more%20common.%20Despite%20the%20higher%20cost%2C%20we%20were%20committed%20to%20sustainability%20and%20refused%20to%20compromise%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20contributing%20to%20the%20growing%20plastic%20problem%2C%20we%20created%20biodegradable%20scoops%20that%20would%20break%20down%20naturally%20into%20the%20soil%2C%20reducing%20waste%20and%20supporting%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosmix%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20in%20the%20wellness%20industry%20to%20embrace%20this%20innovative%20packaging%20solution.%20The%20biodegradable%20scoops%20became%20a%20talking%20point%20for%20the%20brand%2C%20and%20they%20differentiated%20themselves%20from%20other%20protein%20supplement%20brands%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20listen%20to%20our%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vibha.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20asked%20us%20not%20to%20send%20scoops%20with%20our%20products%2C%20while%20others%20preferred%20having%20them.%20We%20had%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20that%20worked%20for%20everyone.%E2%80%9D%20After%20much%20consideration%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20develop%20scoops%20made%20from%20biodegradable%20material%2C%20which%20uses%20husks%20and%20starch.%20These%20scoops%20are%20specifically%20designed%20for%20food%20products%20and%20are%20made%20from%20plant-based%20materials%20that%20naturally%20break%20down%20into%20nutrient-rich%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi